{
  "stem": "26465.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least the people with whom I was, they were very down to earth peasants, working their farms, and cleaning their houses, and being-- being quite cozy in this situation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe that whoever did that were mostly people who worked very hard at destroying people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And their kapos, or henchmen, were taken out from mostly from the prisons so that they could atone for whatever they did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were just exercising their power.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- it was simply, to me, I believe, of course the whole nation has been sort of brainwashed by these politicians.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In May 1945, I was already-- well, on May 20-- 17, the American Army came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in the field.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was running like crazy home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I started-- I heard the staccato of the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I ran to the-- to her place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had my-- even my lunch and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And towards the evening, there was-- there was Army unit came on her yard, quite a lot of military, quite a lot of soldiers around.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they came into the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I have to tell you that, because this is very important.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was alone in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know where the woman was, nor the girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And where the Boris-- Boris went, I don't  know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Maybe he hid too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because to me, he was a-- he was a traitor, collaborator to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because he came voluntarily to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, he was a-- he was a good man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I should not other-- in any other way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Towards me he was all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was going-- I went upstairs to my-- to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I hear the commotion downstairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
